    AdminUI <-->|HTTPS REST / Auth API Key| RustWorker

    RustWorker <-->|Cloudflare Binding| D1Db
    RustWorker <-->|Cloudflare Binding| KVStore

    RustWorker <-->|HTTPS / REST API| StripeAPI
